## Models (API Integration)

**Location**: `apps/{crm,main}/src/modules/{moduleName}/components/models/{name}-model.js`

### Built-in XHR Methods (CRITICAL)
Every model gets: `get`, `add`, `update`, `setup`, `delete`, `all` — NEVER override unless behavior genuinely differs.

`all()` reads from model data and sends as query params:

| Model data key | Backend picks up as |
|---|---|
| `filter` | `$inputs->filter` |
| `search` | `$inputs->modifiers['search']` |
| `dates` | `$inputs->modifiers['dates']` |
| `orderBy` | `$inputs->modifiers['orderBy']` |
| `groupBy` | `$inputs->modifiers['groupBy']` |

```javascript
import { Model } from "@base-framework/base";

export const PostModel = Model.extend({
    url: '/api/post',
    xhr: {
        // Only add LEGITIMATELY custom methods (different URL, FormData, SSE)
        addWithFiles(instanceParams, callBack, files)
        {
            const data = this.model.get();
            const formData = new FormData();
            Object.keys(data).forEach(key =>
            {
                if (key !== 'attachments') formData.append(key, data[key]);
            });
            Array.from(files).forEach(file => formData.append('attachments[]', file));
            return this._post('', formData, instanceParams, callBack);
        },

        sync(instanceParams, callBack, onOpenCallBack)
        {
            const lastId = instanceParams?.lastId || 0;
            const params = lastId ? `lastId=${lastId}` : '';
            return this.setupEventSource('/sync', params, callBack, onOpenCallBack);
        }
    }
});
```

**Do NOT create custom methods for**: filtering, searching, sorting, date ranges, pagination — use built-in `all()` with model data keys.

```javascript
// ✅ CORRECT — change filter and reload
filterByType(type) { this.data.filter = { type }; this.data.xhr.all({}, (r) => { ... }); }
onSearch(q) { this.data.search = q; this.data.xhr.all({}, (r) => { ... }); }
```

## Modules System

```javascript
import { Icons } from "@base-framework/ui/icons";
import { Module } from '../module/module.js';

const routes = Module.convertRoutes([
    { path: '/', import: () => import('./components/pages/home/home-page.js'), title: 'Home' },
    { path: '/settings', import: () => import('./components/pages/settings/settings-page.js'), title: 'Settings' }
]);

const links = [
    { label: 'Home', href: './', icon: Icons.home, mobileOrder: 1, exact: true },
    { label: 'Settings', href: './settings', icon: Icons.settings, mobileOrder: 5 }
];

Module.create({ routes, links });
```

Register in `apps/{crm,main}/src/modules/imported-modules.js`:
```javascript
import "./home/module.js";
```

**Link icon options**: `Icons` (Heroicons SVG), `MaterialSymbols`, or a Material Symbol name string.
